---
import Layout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---
<html lang="en">
  <body>
    <Layout title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION}>
        <h1>Terms and Conditions</h1>

        <p><strong>Article 1 – Definitions</strong><br>
        In these terms and conditions, the following definitions apply:<br>
        <strong>Mameleon</strong>: based in Wijk bij Duurstede, registered with the Dutch Chamber of Commerce.<br>
        <strong>Client</strong>: any natural or legal person who enters into or wishes to enter into an agreement with Mameleon.<br>
        <strong>Products</strong>: materials provided by Mameleon, such as workbooks, cards, online courses, and other tools related to coaching and personal growth.<br>
        <strong>Services</strong>: coaching, training sessions, workshops, lectures, and other related activities.</p>

        <p><strong>Article 2 – Applicability</strong><br>
        These terms and conditions apply to all offers, quotations, agreements, and deliveries of products and services by Mameleon.</p>

        <p><strong>Article 3 – Formation of the Agreement</strong><br>
        An agreement is established once the client gives verbal, written, or digital confirmation of Mameleon’s offer.</p>

        <p><strong>Article 4 – Delivery and Use</strong><br>
        1. Products are delivered as agreed.<br>
        2. Digital materials are for personal use only and may not be distributed, copied, or resold without prior written permission.</p>

        <p><strong>Article 5 – Cancellation and Right of Withdrawal</strong><br>
        1. There is no right of withdrawal for digital products after delivery.<br>
        2. Coaching and training sessions can be canceled free of charge up to 48 hours in advance. Cancellations made after this time will be charged in full.</p>

        <p><strong>Article 6 – Intellectual Property</strong><br>
        All materials provided by Mameleon remain the intellectual property of Mameleon unless otherwise agreed in writing. Commercial use without permission is strictly prohibited.</p>

        <p><strong>Article 7 – Liability</strong><br>
        Mameleon is not liable for any damage resulting from the use of its services or products, unless in cases of intentional misconduct or gross negligence.</p>

        <p><strong>Article 8 – Applicable Law</strong><br>
        Dutch law applies to these terms and conditions. Disputes will be submitted to the competent court in Utrecht, the Netherlands.</p>
    </Layout>
  </body>
</html>